{"tid":319550,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"份intern好廢，好想quit","createTime":"2017-07-13T01:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T11:08:22.000Z","uid":73319,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1b0b7a35683c19a7a0a65320e800247eadebf4","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"低最低工資起馬10蚊<br />\n細公司，返工多數做打雜<br />\n例如：噴油，貼標籤<br />\n<br />\n唔係為fulfill 大學要求唔會做<br />\n依加時數做夠想走，但簽左3個月contract <br />\n<br />\n如果quit 有咩要留意？<br />\n<br />\n有幾個憂慮：<br />\n1）學校要求寫intern report, 要比公司endorse 先，怕佢唔endorse<br />\n2)公司唔比工作證明，唔知intern 工作證明重唔重要<br />\n3）冇今個月人工比，事因合約上佢比我跑嘅工資係用左 「津貼」此字眼，本身最低工資又唔適用於實習員工<br />\n<br />\n求指教"},{"pid":"6a0f23a0a846b43ef6c1534c3c462fc0aa6aa90b","tid":319550,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"081031ca0a017df91dd69f9c420d4de1306c9900","tid":319550,"uid":56498,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"intern係去做打雜架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1847d29a4327768cd76b7a8863ad3e043e0f9d53","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個月霎下眼就過咗啦<br />\n又唔係日日奴役你<br />\n捱埋佢好撚難為你咩</blockquote><br />\n唔重要係冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前一個暑期賺一年洗費<br />\n依加hall fee 都唔夠錢交<br />\nYear 4 又忙，邊有時間搵錢養自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話grad trip, 平時洗費都唔夠"},{"pid":"947dfc6033b51782a0dd06b99adb9072a48e3c27","tid":319550,"uid":40779,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>intern係去做打雜架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主以為去做經理，點人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nintern為嘅係經驗<br />\n屌你求人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5bcea6c70eb40ba3d57187610260da2657f478","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>intern係去做打雜架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主以為去做經理，點人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">intern為嘅係經驗</span><br />\n屌你求人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打雜何來經濟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82507cdeaf8ff345e8e6b0de6cefab1021ff5cd9","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>intern係去做打雜架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主以為去做經理，點人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">intern為嘅係經驗</span><br />\n屌你求人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打雜何來經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打錯"},{"pid":"093def2b5ed535fa62b62ed06acd32f17a02a853","tid":319550,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>intern係去做打雜架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌fg做乜乜trainee都係咁啦，何況煙腸"},{"pid":"342fe11617d47dbe9a16b5f51c09a1f482cbf32f","tid":319550,"uid":40460,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"你唔廢就搵到份有錢嘅intern 啦<br />\n仲好意思嫌棄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812218a911ae0d22145201f29c0d03146acd5311","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"其實份工唔辛苦好輕鬆下，同事唔差<br />\n但屌你老咪人工低撚到<br />\n又冇野學<br />\n<br />\n我都要為自己打算下，搵過份工人工合理<br />\n學唔學到野都係其次"},{"pid":"2899a82bbe187e17db1726bd25a18b40b06e7c4a","tid":319550,"uid":15136,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:11:06.000Z","msg":"收到offer唔知人工既咩？<br />\n而家先黎怨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1570b215fb63bf4afa5329e9a8e9abe19d4b403c","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔廢就搵到份有錢嘅intern 啦<br />\n仲好意思嫌棄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有其他intern 有offer 但簽左contract 廢事麻煩到同事姐<br />\n唔係我返幾日就quit<br />\n人工多唔只一倍"},{"pid":"91911f9ac17fe9c2995ec956bfc9e873943dd85d","tid":319550,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"依家轉你唔怕做唔到report<br />\n你今年無得做report<br />\n下年你要defer喎"},{"pid":"10b1bb6ac34291d0808ff88301c6de02fe495fdf","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到offer唔知人工既咩？<br />\n而家先黎怨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前冇經濟問題<br />\n依加有"},{"pid":"f2cf117c9fd0c6c4e341c25e6976690a63c3c672","tid":319550,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你唔廢就搵到份有錢嘅intern 啦<br />\n仲好意思嫌棄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有其他intern 有offer 但簽左contract 廢事麻煩到同事姐<br />\n唔係我返幾日就quit<br />\n人工多唔只一倍</blockquote><br />\n即係點...宜家quit有人請你做另一份intern?<br />\n宜家依份做咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"6699bf2ec5e00a495d27e40bb1f00da1157b5feb","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家轉你唔怕做唔到report<br />\n你今年無得做report<br />\n下年你要defer喎</blockquote><br />\n所以要睇依加個公司簽唔簽report <br />\n佢endorse 個intern 就完"},{"pid":"a37c9f3872dc64534b49fc2589e38b11bad0f455","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你唔廢就搵到份有錢嘅intern 啦<br />\n仲好意思嫌棄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有其他intern 有offer 但簽左contract 廢事麻煩到同事姐<br />\n唔係我返幾日就quit<br />\n人工多唔只一倍</blockquote><br />\n即係點...宜家quit有人請你做另一份intern?<br />\n宜家依份做咗幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n做左一個半月<br />\n之前d intern reject 曬offer，有$45/hr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗住求其搵份工賺錢"},{"pid":"8a50e2dbcffccb3bb78ac537334c918af83499bb","tid":319550,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"屌㩒錯正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0d421a774befd75bc9cb451bff3c1f3ef838cf","tid":319550,"uid":33222,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"我宜家返緊呢份intern 51蚊一個鐘到，我都覺得少，2x幾蚊一個鐘嘅intern點捱"},{"pid":"1452d01c962ca6f1f604dc6464b50940c0469d18","tid":319550,"uid":104168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:26:10.000Z","msg":"Intern係咁架啦<br />\n就算政府都係得9600一個月<br />\n做做下quit應該都好難比工作證明你<br />\n要fulfill大學要求就做埋佢啦<br />\n你做夠鐘但係中途quit可能都唔當你做過<br />\n等錢洗出張信用卡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有節制之後一定還到"},{"pid":"83b47b2f1ccf86aec445a44ede0964b986bb3318","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Intern係咁架啦<br />\n就算政府都係得9600一個月<br />\n做做下quit應該都好難比工作證明你<br />\n要fulfill大學要求就做埋佢啦<br />\n你做夠鐘但係中途quit可能都唔當你做過<br />\n等錢洗出張信用卡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有節制之後一定還到</blockquote><br />\n有$6000 我都唔會quit 啊<br />\n我9600 一半都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工返到欠債就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1fd2f44099577ada8d7ac251479765733bad63","tid":319550,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Intern係咁架啦<br />\n就算政府都係得9600一個月<br />\n做做下quit應該都好難比工作證明你<br />\n要fulfill大學要求就做埋佢啦<br />\n你做夠鐘但係中途quit可能都唔當你做過<br />\n等錢洗出張信用卡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有節制之後一定還到</blockquote><br />\n有$6000 我都唔會quit 啊<br />\n我9600 一半都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工返到欠債就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪學校介紹果啲，人工低成咁"},{"pid":"439cd1dbcdce14afea8d373bdf6b3d3e4e1572ef","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Intern係咁架啦<br />\n就算政府都係得9600一個月<br />\n做做下quit應該都好難比工作證明你<br />\n要fulfill大學要求就做埋佢啦<br />\n你做夠鐘但係中途quit可能都唔當你做過<br />\n等錢洗出張信用卡先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有節制之後一定還到</blockquote><br />\n有$6000 我都唔會quit 啊<br />\n我9600 一半都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工返到欠債就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪學校介紹果啲，人工低成咁</blockquote><br />\n搵工網搵"},{"pid":"a2fc09df4310a2d641e8713caae4f811fffdb785","tid":319550,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"屌邊度既intern都係打雜架啦"},{"pid":"4c76e545be493131a0f7f6285bd9cf1595dc57f2","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌邊度既intern都係打雜架啦</blockquote><br />\n人工合理打雜冇所謂<br />\n問題係人工最低工資都冇"},{"pid":"da37f442182f49d84be90d2a9d7620a6d4fb7997","tid":319550,"