kquote><br />\n大部份姐 你唔好話你返開嗰啲廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返緊Intern 做緊同同事一樣既野 有時仲要多野做過同事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2a14cc83fca74e06805153bb1276aa00b69d0c","tid":319550,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解覺得你係自己攞黎<br />\n有其他高啲又唔做 而家上黎係度怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔抵幫</blockquote><br />\n唔係怨<br />\n只係想走人姐<br />\n個Post 下半先係重點<br />\n睇下有咩方法quit 好d</blockquote><br />\n咁你仲話無野學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辦公室政治都未識</blockquote><br />\n求其一份工都學到啦<br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你識又上嚟？碌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上嚟就係唔識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下其他人有咩睇法再決定</blockquote><br />\n難怪你學唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當好心同你講多句<br />\n返工就放低你塊死人面<br />\n唔好以為自己係幾咁出眾<br />\n他日你可能成功嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過成功之你都係個正契弟嚟<br />\n不可一世既死𡃁仔我年年都見唔少<br />\n我自己當年都係<br />\n飛黃騰達既我只係見過2個<br />\n繼續係條碌柒咁既就多不勝數<br />\n<br />\n經濟壓力就人人都有<br />\n點死掂佢係你自己既事<br />\n話知你早一份晚一份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到好了解我情況咁<br />\n<br />\n返去做動物傳心師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea577ee56cd66a6721f9814d5f5e82972255a516","tid":319550,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"夜晚打兼職搵外快囉"},{"pid":"067b55648b4d93842d55e0176c5462bd69be7278","tid":319550,"uid":26422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:34: